Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:06.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.82,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,A little present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:12.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Were you here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:19.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't be dumb. I do go home at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:24.67,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Um, we were thinking of skipping school, as well, and helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just the thought is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:32.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We can't have both Class E and D's class reps be absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.93,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Kotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.42,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Are you getting your sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:41.02,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Are you eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:46.39,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We're looking forward to your birthday the day after tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Will this really all work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.34,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.32,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.79,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Please don't push yourselves too hard, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Does it look like things will end by tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To be honest, I intend to work through the night today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:24.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,In that case—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You were going to say you'll stay, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:38.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you catch a fever or something, the old man will get pissed and might ban me forever from your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:42.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, didn't you work until late last night, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is nothing compared to\Nthe basketball team's workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:55.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay. Then please let me know any time you need a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Man, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everyone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.75,Default,Man,0,0,0,,What we can observe isn't the only universe. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:30.64,Default,Man,0,0,0,,There is a realm that was shed and sealed away while this world was taking form. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.21,Default,Man,0,0,0,,The hidden world. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The hidden world, eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't mind me reading it now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Day before yesterday I saw a rabbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and yesterday a deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:14.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see, so she was quoting the lines from this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.22,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Day before yesterday I saw a rabbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and yesterday a deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.42,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and today, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Who are you? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:14.03,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Why are you here? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was playing and wandered in here. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.60,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kotomi. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You spell Kotomi with three hiragana. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.78,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,When you call me, call me Kotomi-chan. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.76,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh my. We have a cute guest. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's how I met Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Itadakimashou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This is a California poppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This is a pansy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:53.15,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan, since the weather is so nice, why not go play outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,We are outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:03.15,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Outside is beyond the hedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:08.90,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's a very vast world with many things that you don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.91,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's scary, so I don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Day before yesterday I saw a rabbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.74,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and yesterday a deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:18.96,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and today, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi didn't like going outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never saw her other friends visiting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:32.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, can I bring my friends over to your birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I want to celebrate your birthday with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:44.13,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What? A birthday party of someone we don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:47.58,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Isn't it embarrassing to go to a girl's birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:59.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not knowing how I should face her,\NI couldn't bring myself to go to the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:07.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was after dark that I finally came to a conclusion that I had to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:11.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I felt I had to apologize for skipping her birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.38,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I burned it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:58.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I burned Father and Mother's paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:22.02,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,No, there's no reason for you to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:25.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What you burned was something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never saw Kotomi after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:44.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I visited her house several times after that, but never got to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My encounter with Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All the time I spent in the yard…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everything seemed like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:10:00.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And eventually, I forgot everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.36,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Who are you? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.92,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Why are you here? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.42,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I might still be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:22.18,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I always remembered the boy who wandered into the yard. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:29.27,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I really, really liked that boy. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:34.06,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He was my only friend… {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.01,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…so I kept waiting for him. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Day before yesterday I saw a rabbit, {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.87,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and yesterday a deer, {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.79,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and today, you. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.99,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You're Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm here to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.90,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,The sky's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:26.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.18,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:48.81,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Morning, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.48,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Were you all waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.56,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Today's your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:06.96,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:11.06,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,And, about your present…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.78,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,A violin gift certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:19.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's that violin you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:23.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We intended to give it to you, but it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:28.23,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It can be repaired, but it couldn't be fixed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:32.27,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,When it comes back fixed, we'll give it to you, so hold on to that until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.28,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.90,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Ichinose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:46.28,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Wonderful. I see you're willing to come to school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.08,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Sensei, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.00,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:57.30,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Your godfather is going to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.24,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,He said there's something he wants to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He's not that bad of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You actually know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's have him come to the drama club's club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That way you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:22.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We'll be there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's meet him, Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:28.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.54,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Kotomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.72,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'm glad I could see her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's Father's suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:59.13,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,This arrived at the research lab late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:04.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I opened it and confirmed that it belonged to Dr. Ichinose,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.30,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,and told myself I had to give this to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Is the paper inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Open it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're with you, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.99,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,He's right. Fight, Kotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.91,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.54,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:07.70,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,If you… this suitcase…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:12.91,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“If you find this suitcase, please take it to our daughter.”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:17.84,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The signature is the initials of\NIchinose Koutarou and Ichinose Mizue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:20.54,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,In other words, Kotomi-kun's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:26.17,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This is how they always signed co-authored papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:29.20,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The suitcase belonged to the Ichinoses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:34.10,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It must have drifted to shore after a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:39.93,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Someone found the suitcase, opened it, and saw the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.15,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Then passed it on to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:48.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,This suitcase must have gotten passed on from one person to another like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:54.53,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,There is evidence of several people touching up the bear and suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:16:03.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You probably don't know what was inside the envelope you burned, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.63,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,The paper Father and Mother wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.97,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,There was never a second copy of the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:22.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\fscx100}Your father was editing the paper until the very last moment, so he mustn't have had time to make a second copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.90,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Then what was inside the envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:30.26,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Inside was a catalogue of teddy bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:35.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You probably would never have believed me if I had told you this any earlier than today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:38.73,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,but I think you'll believe me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:41.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I still remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:45.04,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,“For the first time, my daughter said what she wants.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.74,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Your father had such a happy face as he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:53.54,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But the paper should have been inside this suitcase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father and Mother's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:58.77,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Read it please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.23,Note,,0,0,0,,Dear Kotomi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.70,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“Dear Kotomi.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.63,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“The world is beautiful.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.57,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“Even when it seems to be filled with sadness and tears…”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.14,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This is Father's handwriting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.21,Note,,0,0,0,,To our cute Kotomi, Happy Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:35.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Your Father and Mother threw away everything else inside, including the paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:38.43,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,and instead placed the bear and the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:48.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Your parents were trying to describe the world's origin as beautifully, purely, and concisely as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:54.73,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,But I've never seen anything more beautiful than the words in that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:18:01.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Your Father and Mother were wishing for your happiness until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.63,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I've been waiting all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:13.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I've been crying inside the house all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:18.35,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Then, Tomoya-kun came to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:23.20,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm very blessed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Very, very blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:27.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.48,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father… Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That suitcase must have traveled the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Cities in the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,islands of ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:57.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,steep mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and green plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,From one person to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was passed on with care.
