Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.70,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Dear Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.69,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,The world is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:20:00.54,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Even when it seems to be filled with sadness and tears, open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Do what you wish to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.44,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Become what you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:11.20,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:17.50,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Don't rush, and take your time in becoming an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:29.25,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,He's a bear we found at a gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:34.34,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,We looked around many places, and he was the biggest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.76,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,We didn't have time\Nand couldn't send him from the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.68,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Our cute Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:46.44,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:14.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.75,Default,All,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We invited Sunohara and Miyazawa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They're getting the food right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:35.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My father and mother will come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:38.54,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,When everyone gets here,\Nlet's have the presentation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Okay. I made some sweets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:45.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet you made too much again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.37,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Today, it doesn't matter how much you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:53.77,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Like the concert we had, I gathered a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:57.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, that'll be too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will they all fit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.66,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My garden is big, after all.
