Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:44.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Basketball…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Between the two of us, that'd be your field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Is there a meaning to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.19,0:23:53.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to cry…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:00.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:06.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:09.07,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're not going to back down now, are you?
